doc.after: Some of Alaska s popular annual events are the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race that starts in Anchorage and ends in Nome World Ice Art Championships in Fairbanks the Blueberry Festival and Alaska Hummingbird Festival in Ketchikan the Sitka Whale Fest and the Stikine River Garnet Fest in Wrangell The Stikine River attracts the largest springtime concentration of American bald eagles in the world
